OL,3,CBarton House: Hundreds forced to
OL,4,Cleave homes as major structural fault
OL,5,Cfound at Bristol tower block
OL,7,FWatch Richard Payne's report.
OL,9,FResidents living in a tower block in
OL,10,FBristol have been told to leave their
OL,11,Fhomes due to a "major structural
OL,12,Ffault".
OL,14,FBarton House, in Barton Hill, is
OL,15,Fcurrently being evacuated. ITV News
OL,16,Funderstands there are fire safety
OL,17,Fconcerns relating to the building.
OL,19,FIt means as many as 400 people -
OL,20,Fincluding 100 children - will need to
OL,21,Ffind a new place to stay.
